dataIdInfo.idAbs: The dataset represents the communes and quarters of Cambodia. The dataset was obtained from the Department of Geography of the Ministry of Land Management, Urbanization and Construction in 2008 and unofficially updated in 2014 according to sub-decrees on administrative modifications. Data provided by WFP - VAM unit Cambodia.

Consts.useLimit: See the COD/FOD Registry Terms of Use. This does not replace any terms of use information provided with the dataset.

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated reference name field 2. 9 Admin3 names converted to Proper Case: "Banteay Meas Khang lech", "lek Muoy", "OMal", "Preaek A chi", "Preaek Ta kov", "Sdach Kong Khang lech", "Stueng Mean chey", "Trapeang chorng", "wat Kor" 3. Double space error fixed in Admin3 name "Angk Romeas". 4. Found and fixed 23 Overlap Errors and 2 Gap Errors. 5. Projection changed from undefined to 'GCS_WGS_1984'.
